et  july  gavin breaks the mold gavin los angeles times p c   a b hopper hedda  sep  looking at hollywood john gavin signs pact to do outside films tv chicago tribune p c   zylstra freida  feb  salad maker makes debut in new tv series tonight chicago tribune p b   macminn aleene  mar  gavins first series los angeles times p e   finnigan joseph  dec  millions utilized on pilots for new season los angeles times p b   martin betty  june  gavin signs universal pact los angeles times p d   martin betty  feb  movie call sheet john gavin set for role los angeles times p c   thomas kevin  mar  pussycat pussycat opens multiple run los angeles times p f   page eleanor  jan  paging people a stylish benefit chicago tribune p n   evans peter  july  has time banked the fires of sexy agent  banking the fires of agent  los angeles times p s   wood thomas  nov  movies search overroger moore the new james bond the new bond los angeles times p s   john gavin biography screen actors guild sagaftraorg   zyda joan  sep  dennis weaver seeks actor guild presidency actors guild los angeles times p c   gold aaron  may  tower ticker chicago tribune p b   drake sylvie  sep  will they love lucie too more stage news more stage news more stage news more stage news more stage news los angeles times p m   sullivan dan  sep  local girl makes good in seesaw lucie in seesaw los angeles times p f   colander pat  aug  jerrys just jake with john chicago tribune p b   gavin as grant a test of taste mann roderick los angeles times current file los angeles calif  july  g  bustamante jorge  mar  gavins selection a slap in mexicos face los angeles times p c   a b alan c miller gavin weighs gop bid for us senate  politics the former actor and ambassador meets with leaders who feel the declared candidates cant win los angeles times  august  accessed  november   vernon scott  mar  a look at john gavin at home chicago tribune p d   february   the daily herald from provo utah · page   profile in people magazine  nancy brooks gavin leaving arco to take post at univisa los angeles times  april  accessed  november   business people gavin quits arco for univisa satellite by daniel f cuff and stephen phillips new york times  april  accessed  november   john gavin at biographycom  john gavin biography at americanambassadorsorg  biography at business week accessed  november   hopper hedda  july  laurence olivier shuns  to play caesar chicago daily tribune p b   sam staggs born to be hurt the untold story of imitation of life macmillan  accessed  november   hopper hedda  july  looking at hollywood ski murder film will star john gavin chicago daily tribune p    hopper hedda  january  zugsmiths next big film to be the unvanquished chicago daily tribune p b   scheuer philip k  august  john gavin to join wayne in alamo sessue menaces swiss family son of god at  million los angeles times p    tony curtis set for  new films robert mulligan to direct star in two  rat race editing is completed new york times  january  p    scheuer philip k  apr  pawnbroker will be steiger vehicle mcgiver back at funmaking curious case of lotte lenya los angeles times p c   eugene archer  august  new york lures movie producer ross hunter to work here on films and a musical new york times p    hopper hedda  august  peter falk shelley winters to star in the balcony actor turns down film with bardot chicago daily tribune p b   howard thompson  april  titanus films denies reports that production is falling off new york times p    hopper hedda  september  looking at hollywood john gavin signs pact to do outside films tv chicago tribune p c   taylorburton film fun for rod taylor i remain healthy he says has nine pictures lined up hopper hedda los angeles times  february  p d   scheuer p k  aug  rita hayworth will return in circus los angeles times current file retrieved from httpsearchproquestcomdocview  scheuer philip k  january  revived burlesque shows infirmities the gags and the gals best part of ucla production los angeles times p c   alpert don  may  cyd charisse strange things can happen to a pretty girl acting overseas los angeles times p l  external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to john gavin john gavin on imdb john gavin at the internet broadway database john gavin – so suave diplomatic posts preceded by julian nava us ambassador to mexico – succeeded by charles j pilliod jr v t e presidents of the screen actors guild ralph morgan  eddie cantor  robert montgomery  ralph morgan  edward arnold  james cagney  george murphy  robert montgomery  ronald reagan  walter pidgeon  leon ames  howard keel  ronald reagan  george chandler  dana andrews  charlton heston  john gavin  dennis weaver  kathleen nolan  william schallert  edward asner  patty duke  barry gordon  richard masur  william daniels  melissa gilbert  alan rosenberg  ken howard  gabrielle carteris  authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n isni     gnd  sudoc  bnf cbz data retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlejohngavinoldid categories  birthsliving peopleamerican male film actorsamerican male stage actorspresidents of the screen actors guildhispanic and latino american politicianshispanic and latino american male actorsamerican people of mexican descentamerican people of irish descentamerican politicians of mexican descentamerican actorpoliticiansambassadors of the united states to mexicocalifornia republicansunited states navy officersstanford university alumnimale actors from los angelesamerican male actors of mexican descentactivists from californiahidden categories pages using infobox officeholder with ambassador from or minister fromall articles with unsourced statementsarticles with unsourced statements from october articles with ibdb linkswikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with lccn identifierswikipedia articles with isni identifierswikipedia articles with gnd identifierswikipedia articles with bnf identifiers navigation menu personal tools not lo