y morris west – film was never made  heller in pink tights – gavin had talks with george cukor to play a role but he did not appear in the final film  the alamo – meant to play captain dickinson for john wayne – the role was played by ken curtis  the wine of youth – to co star with tony curtis – film was never made  a gathering of eagles – originally announced as rock hudsons costar – rod taylor took the role a remake of the dark angel for producer ross hunter to star with rock hudson and possibly ingrid bergman – film was never made  the challenge – a swashbuckling spoof from titanus studios in italy – the film kept getting pushed back and was never made  night call – based on three stories in the book the man nobody knows by b traven who wrote the treasure of the sierra madre to be shot in mexico biography of simon bolivar   assassination in rome – originally the assassins a chase melodrama to be shot in spain with vittorio gassman cyd charisse and lilo pulver starring gavin as an american newspaperman – gavin pulled out after a disagreement and was replaced by hugh obrian select theatre creditsedit the fantastiks  – pepermille playhouse seesaw  with lucie arnaz – broadway and a tour referencesedit  stars in blue referenced below page  states that gavins mother married ray gavin who adopted john the internet movie data base says that herald ray golenor changed the family name to gavin retrieved february    a b wise james e  rehill anne collier stars in blue movie actors in americas sea services naval institute press p   a b c hopper hedda  july  he never left home los angeles native john gavin wanted no part of pictures so producers beat a path to his door chicago daily tribune p f   richard l coe  june  an artist is at work the washington post times herald p b   a b c joe finnigan  nov  false richboy tag perils film career gavin claims the washington post times herald p g   a b c d e thomas kevin  june  gavin gets down to business los angeles times p d   thomas m