os angeles times  april  accessed  november   business people gavin quits arco for univisa satellite by daniel f cuff and stephen phillips new york times  april  accessed  november   john gavin at biographycom  john gavin biography at americanambassadorsorg  biography at business week accessed  november   hopper hedda  july  laurence olivier shuns  to play caesar chicago daily tribune p b   sam staggs born to be hurt the untold story of imitation of life macmillan  accessed  november   hopper hedda  july  looking at hollywood ski murder film will star john gavin chicago daily tribune p    hopper hedda  january  zugsmiths next big film to be the unvanquished chicago daily tribune p b   scheuer philip k  august  john gavin to join wayne in alamo sessue menaces swiss family son of god at  million los angeles times p    tony curtis set for  new films robert mulligan to direct star in two  rat race editing is completed new york times  january  p    scheuer philip k  apr  pawnbroker will be steiger vehicle mcgiver back at funmaking curious case of lotte lenya los angeles times p c   eugene archer  august  new york lures movie producer ross hunter to work here on films and a musical new york times p    hopper hedda  august  peter falk shelley winters to star in the balcony actor turns down film with bardot chicago daily tribune p b   howard thompson  april  titanus films denies reports that production is falling off new york times p    hopper hedda  september  looking at hollywood john gavin signs pact to do outside films tv chicago tribune p c   taylorburton film fun for rod taylor i remain healthy he says has nine pictures lined up hopper hedda los angeles times  february  p d   scheuer p k  aug  rita hayworth will return in circus los angeles times current file retrieved from httpsearchproquestcomdocview  scheuer philip k  january  revived burlesque shows infirmities the gags and the gals best part of ucla production los angeles times p c   alpert don  may  cyd charisse strange things can happen to a pretty girl acting overseas los angeles times p l  external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to john gavin john gavin on imdb john gavin at the internet broadway database john gavin – so suave diplomatic posts preceded by julian nava us ambassador to mexico – succeeded by charles j pilliod jr v t e presidents of the screen actors guild ralph morgan  eddie cantor  robert montgomery  ralph morgan  edward arnold  james cagney  george murphy  robert montgomery  ronald reagan  walter pidgeon  leon ames  howard keel  ronald reagan  george chandler  dana andrews  charlton heston  john gavin  dennis weaver  kathleen nolan  william schallert  edward asner  patty duke  barry gordon  richard masur  william daniels  melissa gilbert  alan rosenberg  ken howard  gabrielle carteris  authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n isni     gnd  sudoc  bnf cbz data retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlejohngavinoldid categories  birthsliving peopleamerican male film actorsamerican male stage actorspresidents of the screen actors guildhispanic and latino american politicianshispanic and latino american male actorsamerican people of mexican descentamerican people of irish descentamerican politicians of mexican descentamerican actorpoliticiansambassadors of the united states to mexicocalifornia republicansunited states navy officersstanford university alumnimale actors from los angelesamerican male actors of mexican descentactivists from californiahidden categories pages using infobox officeholder with ambassador from or minister fromall articles with unsourced statementsarticles with unsourced statements from october articles with ibdb linkswikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with lccn identifierswikipedia articles with isni identifierswikipedia articles with gnd identifierswikipedia articles with bnf identifiers navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces 