rldleading technology firms he served as the chief financial officer senior vice president and treasurer at cambridge technology partners massachusetts inc from february  to december  mr gavin managed all worldwide financial functions of cambridge technology partners including investor relations activities information systems and real estate he served as a private investor from january  to april  prior to joining cambridge technology partners massachusetts inc in february  he spent twelve years with data general corporation where he served as the chief financial officer and vice president since january  and corporate controller from october  to january  and vice president and treasurer from january  to october  he served ten years with pricewaterhousecoopers in various accounting and audit positions including serving as senior manager in charge of multinational audits he has been an independent director at varonis systems inc since january  he has been director of broadsoft inc since march  qliktech inc since january  he has been a member of supervisory board at cimpress nv since august   he served as a director of qlik technologies inc from february   to august   and ascential software corp from october  to april  he is a certified public accountant mr gavin earned a bs degree in accounting at providence collegeread full background corporate headquarters hudsonweg venlo limburg  lwnetherlandsphone    fax  board members memberships presentdirectorbroadsoft incpresentindependent directorvaronis systems inc education bs providence college other affiliations cambridge technology partners massachusetts incbroadsoft incnavisite incascential software corpdata general corporationbladelogic incprovidence collegevaronis systems incqliktech incqlik technologies inc annual compensation there is no annual compensation data available stocks options exercisable optionsexercisable options valueunexercisable optionsunexercisable options valuetotal value of optionstotal number of op